                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by name",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by category type: employee_task, client_request, price_offer, contract, meeting",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "execute_type",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by execute_type: parallel, sequence",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get list of procedure settings (WorkFlows) with their parent procedure settings only.\n\n**Important:** The `procedure-settings` array inside each WorkFlow contains ONLY parent rows (`parent_id = NULL`). Child internal procedures are NOT included here — use `/procedure-settings/{id}/internal-procedures` to get children."
